    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This driver-spec example features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The chassis retains its legendary balance with refreshed bushings and a responsive steering rack. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved performance car, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain tight and track-ready. A purist\u2019s machine that prioritizes tactile feedback and mechanical integrity.",
