      "description": "This premium executive sedan strikes an excellent balance between sophisticated style and dependable performance. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, with only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, you will find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather upholstery with light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, consistent with careful use. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium surround-sound system and navigation, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly; it has been strictly maintained with a full service history available. Equipped with new tires and recently replaced brake rotors, this car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It offers a refined driving experience for anyone seeking luxury without the new-car price tag.",
